➜套套第一人，如何死在史上最冷门又惊悚的酷刑下
http://www.sohu.com/a/423415203_624188	22922
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201009/d46c7762e6b642cbb7366fa40f32521d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一提起酷刑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大部分人脑袋里蹦出的就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>凌迟处死、五马分尸、剥皮腰斩</strong>什么的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但其实</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">历史的长河中还深藏着一种</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冷门的酷刑叫做</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>抢·救</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201009/dc1da4387b2349cf88b4dd58a0017306.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小查理</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身为国王<strong>查理一世</strong>的大儿子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本该过着无忧无虑的生活</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
