</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">坐等老爹退休</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">安心<strong>子承父业</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201009/ea3139fd370e45568e1beae68555a5fc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大查理和<strong>国会</strong>老看不对眼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搞得英国内战</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最终</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以<strong>大查理拿下两个第一的奖杯</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>小查理哭着跑去法国</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">作为内战结束</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201009/7a00f2d31ed64e17aebaca6ff90f5233.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">新国王一上任</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就搞<strong>禁止娱乐活动</strong>这种事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">惹得大家很不爽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是小查理的机会来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大家决定找他回来<strong>继承王位</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201009/44084a5e45a04b529d32ad5e7e513d72.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接当英格兰国王不太行</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟人民的力量也有限</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是先迂回操作</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">推举小查理成为<strong>苏格兰国王</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成为了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>查理二世</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当上苏格兰国王的查理二世</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心里只想着赶紧夺回老家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是带着军队就是<strong>冲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而那些被禁娱乐活动的民众</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也十分支持</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">义愤填膺的加入战斗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就在这天时地利人和中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">战争不负众望地——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201009/db616c66511c415f8f6d66c391204592.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">整个军队</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就查理二世一个逃了出来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还被以1000磅黄金的报酬悬赏捉拿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201009/b168f6567d51494da0e8abefbe77377e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">靠着一手<strong>爬树技能</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">查理二世躲过了搜捕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">保住了老爹亲自拿下的两个第一成就</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后靠着支持者的帮助</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">假扮成<strong>水手</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">混去了法国</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201009/2116b859cba84a1caede550dd182a45a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没想到<strong>法国也收到了悬赏令</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一见到他就立刻<strong>驱逐出境</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没办法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">查理二世只好跑去<strong>西班牙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">混点资助后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">继续在欧洲各国穷游</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">企图遇见真心人助他夺回英格兰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201009/2edeac40e715474aa0d376709c7df2fd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可惜的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大家对这流浪国王都没啥兴趣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">顶多打发点钱就让他走了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这并没有打击到查理二世</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201009/69409b3971ea446abcd4118c94b1680f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>享乐主义</strong>的他</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">即便穷困潦倒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">常年过着吃了上顿没下顿的生活</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但在拿到钱的第一时间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他依旧选择——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>立马花光</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201009/4777d2f4fb944c11b58d6ba3cce1401e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就这么过了<strong>7年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">事情总算发生了转机</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201009/120b9171c88b468691513df6e9456fac.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">新继任的国王名望不足</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">压不住那些个叛逆的心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是大家伙儿决定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接把查理二世请回来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>31岁的查理二世</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>终于当上了英格兰国王</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201009/db5c0eb2483649bbbfe634d316d8e18c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">回来后的查理二世深知人民述求</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>立马取消了“禁欲制度”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让人民重新呼吸上了快乐自由地空气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因此深受民众的喜爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被亲切地称为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“快活王”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201009/b590d21ec73b4b4980648bc0e428ffad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身为快活王</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他以身作则<strong>天天快活</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身后情妇无数</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">光是和情妇的私生子就有14个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但面对皇后的不孕不育</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他也依旧不离不弃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201009/e5ed8031ecbe40cbaeec3750b51c2cf5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而为了查理二世运动过程的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">健康与舒适</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">御医<strong>约瑟夫·康德姆</strong>（Joseph Condom）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还利用<strong>小羊的盲肠</strong>为其发明定制了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">船新版本</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>小羊肠套套</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它舒适温和柔软</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让查理二世人生更加快乐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为这个发明</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">御医不仅得到了<strong>骑士勋爵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此后的安全套也以它命名为——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Condom</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201009/7b445a3e2fcf42cbba20218444db8c39.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有个词说得好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>乐极生悲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">快乐的时光总是短暂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而生病总是来得猝不及防</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201009/3a6347d599674281bf9a6262d51b8cfb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">国王生病可是件大事儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">医生们聚集在一起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">进行了严肃又专业的紧急会诊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一致得出了结论</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201009/ce3c2f3d03834f6caaab8cc334dda5a4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">讨论结束后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">医生们开始了对查理二世的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抢救</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你也知道的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在那个年代</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>放血是常规治疗手段</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鉴于国王病情有点严重</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">医生当即决定多放点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就<strong>400ml</strong>吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201009/28c2f73576b14b448eb645acb59e5f30.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">放完了400ml</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">医生们一看</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这好像没啥用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>遂再放了200ml</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看到查理二世略显贫血</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">精神不佳的样子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">医生们拿出了自己的大宝贝<strong>金属锑</strong>——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201009/718b728a183d4718ab67718bf123db50.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>金属锑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">元素符号<strong>Sb</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这下你骂人就可以用：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“你这个元素周期表第51位”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然早在<strong>古埃及</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">锑就在化妆品界有一席之地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但这并不代表它很安全</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相反它是<strong>有毒的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而医生给查理二世服用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也只是为了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>催吐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201009/c4d083263644412fb730a512deb6f808.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">血也放了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吐也吐了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">按道理体内液体应该很平衡了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可查理二世<strong>依旧没啥起色</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201009/dabe74eeb8694f368b76ebb17d8cfad7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身为医生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">病人都没放弃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们怎能先说不行</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是乎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们用<strong>茴香、肉桂、豆蔻、紫罗兰、</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>甜菜根、盐</strong>等调制出的料理药水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开始给查理二世——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>灌肠</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201009/d844e58e0c4e435fbdaf032f1d069fbb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也不知道是不是真的没辙了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">医生们开始了更加</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>严（自）谨（由）的发挥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">剃光了查理二世的头发</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用水洗干净头皮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后<strong>烫出血泡</strong>再<strong>挤掉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201009/ef37a951bdd348208389ada2687284fa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秉承着做事有头有尾的精神</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们同步在查理二世的脚上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抹上了<strong>鸽子屎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以及用<strong>嚏根草</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刺激国王鼻孔让国王打喷嚏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>但国王</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>依旧没什么好转</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201009/a50cf45590934ffeb69131082b5ed1f9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们拿出了<strong>40</strong>滴</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从<strong>人类头盖骨</strong>中提取的精华液</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">配合一块<strong>山羊的胃结石</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">混合后给国王服用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看着查理二世欲哭无泪的面庞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">医生欣喜地告诉民众</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201009/a633d95b543d4a208137b9ce66fab77a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最终</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在医生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">竭（丧）尽（心）全（病）力（狂）的救治下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">查理二世不负众望地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不治身亡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">传闻在生命的最后一刻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可爱的快活王还不忘安慰到医生们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">麻烦大家这么久了，真是辛苦了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201009/9a0c968f1d084cebbbac4c5a5c54355e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">医生不知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>为什么在如此先进的操作下</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>国王没有活下来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">国王也不知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>为什么在如此丧病的操作下</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>自己还坚持了好几天</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那也都不重要了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201009/94fb655049634952b50ef720be3621fc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本文系【朕说】原创内容</p>
